   <sense group="1" n="1" name="admit to wrongdoing with expectation of punishment" type="">
      <commentary>
       NOTE: Compare to sense 3. In this sense the thing being confessed is
       always a negative idea or action that could have some type of repercussion
      </commentary>
      <examples>
        A Michigan man accused of murdering his wife confessed to the crime.
        The suspect has confessed to planting the bomb on a German train.
        The students confessed to eating the last cookie.
      </examples>
